data.description: Welcome to your dream home in a quiet neighborhood with sidewalks, where charm meets modern comfort! This delightful residence features a spacious corner lot, perfect for play and relaxation. Inside, enjoy the open-concept living area with recessed lighting, a stylish kitchen island, and a thoughtful split floor plan for added privacy. The master suite boasts a double vanity sink, adding a touch of luxury to your daily routine. Built just two years ago, this home offers a fresh, modern ambiance, providing peace of mind and a warm welcome to your new haven!
